#: ../../source/faq/hybrid-application.rst:2
msgid "Hybrid application"
msgstr "混合应用"

#: ../../source/faq/hybrid-application.rst:4
msgid ""
"The hybrid application is an application that listens to HTTP requests,as"
" well as makes use of the connected microservices. The "
"``INestApplication`` can be combined with the endless number of the "
"``INestMicroservice`` instances through ``connectMicroservice()`` method."
msgstr ""

